title: The Trouble with Truth
description: The JLA find themselves in danger of losing Wonder Woman when the goddess Athena comes to Earth with an offer Diana can't refuse, filling the position of the Goddess of Truth on Mt. Olympus.

title: Roundabout Part 1
description: Forever Knight finally assembles his Round Table of young but super-powerful Knights, including— Ben?! With Ben's help, Forever Knight leads his new minions in an all-out attack on a Particle Accelerator - his true intention to transform it into a Time Machine and conquer history!

title: Hurricane Chata
description: When V & V discover that Chata's emotions control the water in the lake, they use it to their advantage and start their own wave pool business.

title: Justice League's Next Top Talent Idol Star: Second Greatest Team Edition
description: The Justice League holds another talent competition to find the second best superhero team in the world. The competition heats up and the Titans must find a way to beat the Hive Five.

title: La Dama
description: Los niños descubren que Papá se ha vestido como una mujer para conocer amigos.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Babysitting Bedlam/Rubbed the Wrong Way
description: Rubbed the Wrong Way: After a Bakugan field errupts the town kids stampede to get their own Bakugan but when the field is contaminated Lia must save the day./Babysitting Bedlam: Dan and Wynton meet a strange boy who leads them into an underground maze where they discover the boy's Bakugan has been enslaved.

title: Guardians of Sunshine
description: Finn and Jake go into BMO to defeat an evil Big Boss.

title: The Schooling
description: Gumball and Darwin are at the convenience store considering playing truant. Larry warns them that if they don't take their education seriously they'll end up like him. To prove his point, Larry lets Gumball and Darwin work some of his many roles to make them appreciate the value of a good education.

title: Two Sides of the Coin/The Race for Gold
description: Two Sides of the Coin: The AO and Magnus take parallel tracks to retrieve the same piece of data, one that promises a breakthrough in the Bakugan phenomenon./The Race for Gold: When the AO seek out a mythical, lost Bakugan, they get more than they bargained for when Magnus is on the trail of this new discovery, too.

title: Saving Faith
description: Lloyd and his team plot to take control of the Oni Titan. Meanwhile in the First Realm, the Ninja fall into Iron Baron's clutches and an old master returns.

title: Alone Quest
description: Craig has an "emergency" leaving Kelsey alone at the Stump.

title: Bring Me the Spark of Optimus Prime Part 1
description: The Decepticons compete to be the first to bring Megatron Optimus Prime's spark while Hot Rod chases the "Moon Cheetah."

title: Hawkodile Sensei
description: On a routine mission, Hawkodile finds some defenseless chipmunks that imprint on him.​ ​The bird bodyguard takes it upon himself to become their Sensei teach the younglings his warrior ways, but Unikitty worries his training is too intense. Will Hawkodile's "all work, no play" lifestyle push the chipmunks too far?

title: The Gilded Path
description: The headquarters to the resistance is breached and Lloyd scrambles to avoid capture. Meanwhile, the Ninja are caught by Heavy Metal, but find an unlikely ally.

title: Suerte
description: When Vic cheats on an enchanted board game, the malevolent characters come to life, and it's up to V & V to figure out how to put them back in the game.

title: Let's Team Up Because We Aren't Bad Friends
description: The Warriors fear that they've been ignoring their pals, so they team up with Witchy Simone and Noville for a BIG MISSION, only to discover that their friends aren't into it anymore.

title: Block Party
description: Apple and Onion have to outwit a mean duck who's taken over their building's roof.

title: Subterranean Homesick Blues/Honey Struck
description: Subterranean Homesick Blues: The AO return home to learn that no time has passed but they soon discover their knowledge of brawling has gotten years more advanced./Honey Struck: After Strata is sent packing the AO discover that they have picked up a hitchhiker a Panda-like Bakugan who is nothing but sticky trouble.

title: Fathers and Friends/Midsummer Nightmare
description: Midsummer Nightmare: Drago and the other AO Bakugan face an unseen threat with earth shattering power only to be left wondering if it was all a dream./Father's and Fiends: Osamu Kazami comes to take his son Shun back home and finds a defiance he hadn't counted on.

title: The Mystery of the Timekeeper
description: When the Time Keeper goes missing, Craig and his friends take up the task of helping kids get home in time for dinner.

title: El eslabon mas debil
description: Lloyd le paga con la misma moneda a Harumi para quitarle el poder a su padre, y los Ninjas aprenden lo que se necesita para ser un Cazador de Dragones.

title: Hostile Take Over/The Big Bounce
description: Hostile Take Over: After more unsuccessful attempts to harness Core Cell energy the AO must battle their own Bakugan with AAAnimus tech in order to save them./The Big Bounce: The AO confront Philomena with concerns about her control over the Core Cell energy and are fired in the most unceremonious of manners.

title: Pancake's Bus Tour
description: Apple and Onion go on a guided bus tour as part of their plan to get Apple's shoe back.

title: Bienvenido a la Zona Zombozo
description: Durante tiempos medievales, el equipo Tennyson debe esforzarse por recordar que no están en el pasado, sino en una feria renacentista, idonde el "Rey Zombozo" ha hipnotizado a sus invitados para que crean que viven en el pasado!

title: Sea of Tranquility Part 1
description: Optimus Prime and the Autobots battle Megatron and the Deceptions on Earth's Moon.

title: Loteria
description: Cuando Vic hace trampa en un juego de mesa encantado, los malvados personajes cobran vida, y V y V son los responsables de averiguar cómo volver a ponerlos en el juego.

title: Hotdog's Movie Premiere
description: Apple and Onion square off against a no-nonsense security guard after they're banned from the premiere of their friend Hot Dog's new movie.

title: Breakup
description:
Feeling left out, Adorabat wishes Mao Mao and Badgerclops would spend less time with each other and more time with her. When she gets
what she wishes for and accidentally breaks up their friendship, only the secret of their past can bring them back together.

title: Unboxing Part 1
description: Axel ventures into his uncle's strictly off-limits basement lab in hopes of fixing a broken toy and ends up unleashing living ones instead: the renegade Madcap and a whole team of superpowered toys dedicated to stopping him!

title: Attack the Block Party
description: Clarence, Jeff and Sumo investigate a high school party down the street, which they mistake for an alien invasion.

title: Tips
description: Apple and Onion have to find a way to ride the Hot Air Balloon which is in their town for one day only.

title: Stratified/Maze Daze
description: Stratified: The AO embark on a mission into the mysterious labyrinth world of Vestroia to find Strata the Hunter and free the Bakugan he has imprisoned./Maze Daze: Lost in the maze of Vestroia the AO encounter powerful forces that seem to be struggling for control over the alien landscape.

title: Bloqueo de Tránsito
description: Cuando un paso elevado colapsa sobre la autopista, el equipo Tennyson queda varado en un embotellamiento junto con Simon Sez y familia. Pero cuando Ben y Simon se alían para enfrentar juntos al atasco, Simon solo consigue que las cosas sean mucho, pero mucho peores.

title: Matter of the Mind/Core Cell
description: Matter of Mind: Drago leads the Bakugan against the threat of Tiko to protect a powerful energy source called the Core Cell./Core Cell: The AO defend the Core Cell from an attack by Tiko and in a last ditch effort to save it Dan manages to evolve Drago into his L2 form.

title: Nightmare Hospital
description: Steven and Connie sneak into a hospital to recover Rose's Sword.

title: The Mummy's Curse
description: The Baby Bears must return a mummy to its tomb or else they'll be cursed forever.

title: Chill Out
description: Uncle Grandpa takes a kid to the North Pole for an epic snowball battle.

title: Mo' Linguish/Oops I Did It Again
description: Mo' Linguish: Mojo is sentenced to do community service for Townsville and begins teaching English at the Learning Annex. Soon everyone is speaking in circles like Mojo and the town comes to a standstill./Oops I Did It Again: When the Professor realizes that all his successful experiments are actually just accidents, he sets out to do something brilliant on purpose!

title: The Gauntlet Part 1
description: Lord Obsidian unites the Robot Masters against Mega Man and his family for an epic showdown at the Lighthouse.

title: Burger Run/Monkey See, Monkey Don't
description: Burger Run: When the local Burger Joint is being threatened by a rogue Bakugan, Dan steps up to save the day and the burgers!/Monkey See, Monkey Don't: The AO stop neighborhood kids from copycat behavior (namely, using their Bakugan for frivolous reasons).

title: #FightAtTheMuseum
description: Supergirl always relies on her strength, but she'll need more than brawn to stop brainy Catwoman from stealing valuable gems from the local science museum.

title: 4 on 1
description: Onion's fear of crowds threatens his basketball team's success.

title: Mxy's Mix-Up
description: As the Justice League is trying to protect the United Nations from Grodd's gorilla army, Mr. Mxyptlk pops up from the fifth dimension and thinks it would be great fun to put each of the superheroes' brains into another hero's body.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: El club de los solitarios
description: En lugar de celebrar el Día de San Valentín, Vic y Val se atreven a explorar una mansión encantada con sus rivales, Charlene y Piña.

title: Space Invasion
description: A visit from Puddle the alien tests the limit of Oscar's hosting skills.

title: The Shippening
description: When people that barely know each other start falling in love, Gumball thinks he knows who's behind it. He rushes to Sarah's house and finds her writing in a magic notebook that turns everything in it into reality. When everything in Elmore gets crazier and crazier there's only one thing for it: they have to write their way out.

title: Hot Dog estrena su pelicula
description: Cuando unos guardias de seguridad muy serios los echan del estreno de la nueva película de su amigo Hot Dog, Manzana y Cebollín se preparan para pelear.

title: Dog Daze/In Focus
description: Dog Daze: Lightning discovers a new Bakugan, Artulean, leading to an unhealthy rivalry with Howlkor./In Focus: While Lia's newswoman mom does an expose on the AO Strata the Hunter tries to capture Hydorous.

title: The Viewers Decide
description: It's Titans West vs Titans East as the two teams compete for who gets Bumblebee.

title: The Price of Advice
description: After a paper origami fortune teller tells Izzy she's the world's best advice giver, she's determined to prove it.

title: Balloon Boys
description: Vic & Val go on a hot air balloon trip with Sal and compete to be his favorite, but things go awry when they try to use the magical Nazca Lines to their advantage.

title: The Babysitter
description: Vic & Val want to sneak out to a secret fireworks show but are thwarted when their new babysitter, Xochi, outsmarts them at every turn.

title: Lord of the Poppies
description: Grizz and the Poppy Rangers go camping on an island, but they soon find themselves deserted.

title: Musclecup
description: Feeling inadequate as a superhero, Buttercup bulks up…to the max.

title: Ghosthaste
description: Vambre becomes enamored of a poltergeist within Ghost Magisword and Prohyas must save her before his sister becomes a ghost herself!

title: TV Knight 4
description: Batman and Commissioner Gordon go camping but instead of fun outdoor activities they'd rather watch TV.

title: Permanent Retirement
description: Grandpa, Gwen and Ben visit an old maid relative only to find that her retirement community has been overtaken by a shapeshifting aliens called Limax.

title: Mop Forever
description: At Alice's dress-up party the campers are magically turned into their costumes.

title: BBRBDAY
description: When he isn't invited to Beast Boy's birthday party, Robin throws his own party, with special guest Bob Uecker.

title: Exquisite Grandpa
description: Uncle Grandpa has been having some truly bizarre night terrors.

title: The Weakest Link
description: Lloyd turns the tables on Harumi to take his father's power away, and the Ninja learn what it takes to be a Dragon Hunter.

title: Chip's Damage
description: Elodie enlists KO to help figure out what to do about Chip Damage.

title: Dibs Court
description: When a kid claims dibs on the Stump, Craig has no choice but to take them to court. Dibs Court.

title: Memory Lane of Pain
description: While going through the Professor's scrapbook, Bubbles starts to question if she's ever been a hero.

title: Huracan Chata
description: Cuando V y V descubren que las emociones de Chata controlan el agua del lago, deciden sacar ventaja y comienzan su propio negocio de piscinas de olas.

title: Apple's in Trouble
description: Apple is challenged to a fight by a grumpy Cheesesteak, so he and Onion go on a quest to find the source of Cheesesteak's grumpiness.

title: Framing Device/Bad Actors
description: Framing Device: When confronted by China Riot Lia learns to evolve Pegatrix after realizing the true meaning behind her filming obsession./Bad Actors: Dan tries to lie about evolving Drago and gets exposed while the team face off against Duran Dane and his unhappy Bakugan Nillious.

title: Deez Keys
description: Mordecai and Rigby need to make a deal with the scientists to get Benson's car keys back.

title: Encantadas
description: Durante una comida familiar en un campamento forestal, Charmcaster usa su magia para cambiar de lugar con Gwen, pero cuando Ben descubre a "Charmcaster" husmeando, ataca, sin darse cuenta de que en realidad es su hechizada prima.

title: Firstbourne
description: Emperor Garmadon has taken control of Ninjago City where Lloyd retreats to the shadows. Meanwhile, the other Ninja and Young Wu are shipwrecked in the Realm of Oni & Dragon and find they are not alone.

title: Tabes & Charlie
description: Tabes and Charlie team up to find Tabes' missing dog, Kirk.

title: Ninja vs. Lava
description: The ninja find themselves trapped in a pyramid and must escape encroaching lava to warn NINJAGO City of a new Serpentine invasion.

title: Onion Friend
description: Steven and Amethyst visit the strange world of Onion's house.

title: Mask of Power/Story Holes
description:
Mask of Power: Philomena Dusk from AAAnimus Corp. hires Magnus and gives him a control implant to bolster the power of his Bakugan to defeat Dan./Story Holes:  
A cryptic call leads the AO in search of a missing Bakugan but they soon realize the call was actually a test from a mysterious benefactor.

title: Enemy Mime
description: When the Sheriff's Dept fights a monster that copies their every move, they'll have to find a way to fight without fighting.

title: Lonely Haunts Club
description: Instead of celebrating Valentine's Day, Vic & Val take on a dare to explore a haunted mansion with their rivals, Charlene & Pineapple.

title: Death Kwon Do-livery
description: Mordecai and Rigby want to help save Death Kwon Do sensei's life.

title: Franken-Fight
description: Ben hops into the Rustbuggy for a driving lesson along the sand dunes of Cape Cod, but he takes a freaky switchback turn when the Rustbuggy is mutated into a motor-monster by Bootleg, another alien transformation of Kevin 11, with powers similar to Upgrade!

title: Bad Moon Rising Part 2
description: The Autobots work to stop the Moon from crashing into the Earth as Starscream must reckon with betraying Megatron.

title: Carl
description: A pleasant weekend goes awry when a monster attacks.

title: Panda's Birthday
description: For Panda's Birthday, the Bears try to help Panda meet his favorite K-Pop band, Monsta X.

title: Dawn Before Dusk
description: Dawn Before Dusk, Part 1: The AO meet Benton Dusk discovering that their quiet little corner of the world is about to become much, much larger./Dawn Before Dusk, Part 2: Benton Dusk reveals that the AO have been indentified as persons of interest by powerful corporations including Philomena Dusk's AAAnimus.

title: Awesome vs. AAAnimus
description: Awesome V Aaanimus, Part 1: The AO plan on sneaking into AAAnimus and rescuing their Bakugan but are stopped by Benton who offers up an alternate plan./Awesome V Aaanimus, Part 2: The AO team up with Benton Dusk to recapture their stolen Bakugan and free the energy from the Mind Core Cell under the control of AAAnimus.

title: Chips & Ice Cream
description: BMO's favorite entertainers unexpectedly find a new home at the tree house.

title: Diggin' A Hole
description: Uncle Grandpa digs a hole.

title: #ShockItToMe
description: Leslie Willis, the meanest girl in school, becomes a social media sensation by posting mean-spirited videos on her MetropoVids channel, causing Wonder Woman to question the moral integrity of the people who live in the World of Man.

title: The Anybody
description: Gumball wants Clayton to sit his detention for him, so he convinces him it's way more exciting to be take the shapes of other people.  However, Clayton begins imitating people all over town and causing mayhem. Gumball and Darwin have to convince him that the most exciting person to be is himself.

title: High Flying Hostiles/Backfire Brawl
description: High Flying Hostiles: While escorting the Mind Core Cell to AAAnimus Campus, the AO are attacked by Masato Kazami and his Body Guards./Backfire Brawl: Philomena's attempt to refocus the Mind Core Cell's power backfires and the AO must fight their fellow employees inside the AAAnimus Campus.

title: Arrested Development
description: Ben and Rook must stop the evil Robots from Dimension 12 while trapped in their own pre-pubescent bodies, thanks to Ben's childhood rival.  (Introducing Billy Billions.)

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: The Visitor Part 1
description: Bumblebee searches for any information his fellow Autobots might have regarding a strange creature he saw on the Moon.

title: Hot Diggity Doom
description: It's election day in the Candy Kingdom but Princess Bubblegum's attention is diverted by a mysterious presence in the sky.

title: Keen on Keane/Not So Awesome Blossom
description: Keen on Keane: It's Valentine's Day and the girls notice that Ms. Keane is all alone. Time for a little matchmaking, but who will be the lucky fella?/Not So Awesome Blossom: When Blossom's attack plans fail one after the other, she loses confidence in herself as the group's leader.

title: Radio Ninjago libre
description: Lloyd deberá encontrar su voz mientras lidera una pequeña resistencia para capturar las señales de transmisión en Ciudad Ninjago. Mientras tanto en el Primer Reino, el Barón de Hierro lleva a los Ninjas en una cacería de dragones.

title: King of the Zombeez
description: Frostferatu hires the Warriors to rid his castle of Zombeez when Neddy and a power mad zombie-bee queen take over.

title: The Faith
description: Everything in Elmore is suddenly just various shades of grey, and things all over town are going wrong. Gumball and Darwin follow the mayhem and learn that one person was holding the whole town together: Alan. They have to restore his faith in the world to bring color back to Elmore.

title: Hot Air Buffoon/Ploys R' Us
description: Hot Air Buffoon: The Mayor realizes the girls are doing all the work in his city for him. So he mans a hot air balloon and starts fighting crime the old-fashioned way./Ploys R' Us: The girls wake up to find their room filled with toys. They soon figure out that the Professor has been sleepwalking and stealing. Instead of reporting it, the girls take advantage of the situation.

title: Sea of Tranquility Part 2
description: The Autobots struggle to stop the Decepticon's planet-cracking weapon as it targets Earth.

title: #SuperWho?
description: Overwhelmed by the amount of Superman coverage in Metropolis, Supergirl decides to get out there and really show the city what she can do. But when Superman inadvertently puts everyone in harm's way, Supergirl has to decide whether to do what's good for the people or what's good for her ego.

title: La ninera
description: Vic y Val quieren colarse en un espectáculo secreto de fuegos artificiales, pero su plan se ve frustrado cuando su nueva niñera, Xochi, los supera en todo momento.

title: A Real Steal/Lightning Unleashed
description: A Real Steal: Dan embarks on a solo adventure to outdo Magnus's new team of Bakugan Brawlers and winds up having to be saved by them instead./Lightning Unleashed: Lightning uncovers the Mind Core Cell buried beneath the Earth and battles Stata the Hunter in an effort to protect its secret.

title: All Jungled Up/Outer Demons
description: All Jungled Up: Still lost in Vestroia the AO experience mind altering effects of the nearby Core Cell and come face to face with the Bakuzon monster Tiko./Outer Demons: The AO find the doorway out of Vestroia only to learn they have entered a mirror world of their own imagining created by the Core Cell.

title: Frenemies/Strata's Fear
description: Frenemies: Two new Bakugan Brawlers, Shun and Magnus, try out for the AO./Strata's Fear: The AO solve the mystery of a kid's missing Bakugan and meet a Bakugan Hunter named Strata.

title: The Bubbles-Sitters Club
description: Bubbles tries to prove that she's responsible enough to own a dog.

title: A New Life
description: Apple and Onion both leave their homes and follow their dreams to the big city but things don't go quite to plan.

title: Perfect Moment
description: When Hawkodile admits his love for Dr. Fox, Unikitty and the gang become his love gurus to help him confess his feelings for her. Unfortunately, Unikitty's grand plans for the perfect moment of love complicates everything.

title: Breehn Ho
description: Avast mateys! Clarence and Sumo are psyched to play their pirate-themed board game, Thirty Days and Seven Seas, until they learn Jeff has invited boring old Breehn along. After Breehn gets frustrated and leaves, it's up to the three scallywags to rescue Breehn from an intense flood.

title: The Throw Down/Brawl for It All
description: The Throw Down: Lightning reveals his discovery of the Mind Core Cell but the AO arrive only to discover that Magnus has already beaten them to it./Brawl for It All: With both team's Bakugan knocked into a hibernation state by the Mind Core Cell only Dan and Magnus remain locked in a brawl for it all!

title: Lecciones para un maestro
description: Cuando el Barón de Hierro obliga a Wu a tomar la Armadura de Dragón, las cosas no salen como se planearon. En Ninjago, hay un límite de lo que Lloyd puede soportar mientras se aferra a la esperanza del regreso de los Ninjas.

title: #LaDulceJusticia - Primera parte
description: En el episodio estreno de cuatro partes de la serie, seis chicas comunes y corrientes se conocen y descubren que tienen poderes extraordinarios. Deciden unir sus fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: The Exit/The Lost and the Cost
description: The Exit: The AO compete with a rival Brawling team for ViewTube hits leading to a "winner take all" brawl./The Lost and the Cost: Everett Ray, a promotor, tries to get the AO to join an official league for Bakugan Battling.

title: Splitsville
description: The girls learn to appreciate each others's style after having to each fight solo.

title: Camping is In Tents
description: A class camping trip turns into a treasure hunt while Harold is determined to catch Bigfoot and keep everyone safe.

title: Bring Me the Spark of Optimus Prime Part 2
description: Slipstream searches for her missing Seekers while Hot Rod's "Moon Cheetah" chase brings him unexpectedly aboard the Nemesis.

title: The Perfect Team
description: Onion worries his relationship with Apple is in jeopardy when a stray cat enters the picture.

title: Tripped Up/Power Tripp
description: Tripped Up: Dan and Wynton stumble on both a possible hidden location of the Mind Core Cell and Colonel Tripp who wants the energy source for himself./Power Tripp: After a falling out with Dan, Wynton is mind-controlled by Tripp who stages an attack to ignite a war between Brawlers and the Military.

title: The Visitor Part 2
description: Dino-Mode Grimlock careens out-of-control around the Ark after drinking Wheeljack's hyper-fuel.

title: El Tonto
description: Darwin termina en la sala de detención con el Chico Bomba, que decide convertir a Darwin en su nuevo blanco. Sin embargo, el ataque se vuelve en su contra cuando Darwin le arruina la vida.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Susie's Fantastical Scavenger Hunt
description: Oscar and Hedgehog must learn to exist without each other when they are put on different teams during a scavenger hunt.

title: TKO Rules!
description: KO and TKO decide to swap places for the day.

title: Who Took Toast
description: When Toast disappears from Unikitty's party she leads a search to find him and expose the toast-napper.

title: Shun Shine/Ronin Son
description: Shun Shine: The AO want to evolve their Bakugan like Dan did with Drago but only Shun finds a way by tapping into the energy of the Mind Core Cell./Ronin Son: When Shun's cousin Masato Kazami claims Hydorous as his intellectual property the AO must battle to keep their friend by their side.

title: Cabeza de Playa
description: Después de viajar a Tampa Beach, Florida, el equipo Tennyson espera poder descansar y relajarse, pero las tempestades sin temperamento, los Climáticos, tienen otros planes que Ben debe frustrar: iconstruir una nueva base en la playa!

title: Booster's Gold
description: Green Arrow becomes involved with Booster Gold when he discovers that the self-centered superhero has brought dinosaurs back from the past for a money-making venture.

title: 4 a 1
description: El temor de Cebollín a las multitudes amenaza el éxito de su equipo de baloncesto.

title: Never Trust a Human
description: A flashback episode tells the story of Young Wu and Young Garmadon meeting Aspheera and teaching her the secrets of Spinjitzu.

title: Bad Moon Rising Part 1
description: Starscream makes a play for leadership of the Deceptions as the Autobots storm the Decepticon's Moon Base.

title: Birthday
description: Jeff and Sumo expect no one to show at Clarence's birthday party, just like last year. When dozens of kids arrive, the boys struggle to get face time with Clarence, the popular party host.

title: Unboxing Part 2
description: Axel discovers that he can transform into a toy and teams up with his new team of toys to stop Madcap from stealing a Minergy battery.

title: Powerless
description: The ninja rush to the NINJAGO Museum of History to recover a dangerous scroll before it falls into the hands of the Serpentine Sorceress Aspheera.

title: Escalator
description: A trip to the mall turns into a national disaster when Uncle Grandpa and Pizza Steve become stranded on a broken escalator.

title: Duncan Disorderly
description: Duncan escapes during a community walk only to discover he has to babysit Cody and Bridgette.

title: How to Build a Dragon
description: While Lloyd and the rebels celebrate their successful strike against Emperor Garmadon, in the Realm of Oni and Dragon, the Ninja dare an elaborate escape from the clutches of Iron Baron and his Dragon Hunters.

title: Atrapa la Botella
description: Manzana y Cebollín inventan un nuevo juego que atrae una atención inesperada.

title: Keeping It Together
description: Steven and the Crystal Gems revisit the Kindergarten and find a dark secret.

title: K.O. vs Fink
description: When Fink taunts KO for being a momma's boy, he grapples with newfound insecurity about it.

title: Dizzy
description: M and R help Pops get over his fear of public speaking.

title: Fiesta en la Cuadra
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben ser más astutos que un pato malvado que se apoderó del techo de su edificio.

title: El Elegido
description: Tobías intenta ser el mejor amigo de Gumball.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: BatKitty
description: The gang are at the local laundromat cleaning their clothes, when Unikitty finds Batman's uniform mixed in with her clothes.  Intoxicated by the coolness of it, Unikitty takes on the persona of Batman and begins to fight crime.  When she accidentally causes Master Frown to step up his crime game, she will need the help of her friends, dressed as Robin, to stop him.

title: Outfoxed
description: When Rufus and Reg come to swindle the town, Sheriff Mao Mao teaches them a lesson in justice.

title: Red Action 3: Grudgement Day
description: KO and Enid attempt to prevent a mysterious power battle between Rad and Red Action.

title: Bewitched, Bothered and Bothered Some More!
description: Flonk hires the Warriors to make Witch Way change his brother Helmut from a frog back to human.

title: Not Impressed
description: When a Sweetypie isn't impressed with the sheriff dept's antics, our three heroes try everything to win him over.

title: Billy Billones
description: En Aspen, Colorado, Ben, Gwen y el abuelo Max van de excursión para encontrar al Olvideti. Pero cuando se encuentran con la pista artificial de esquí de Billy Billones, Ben debe luchar contra Billy con la ayuda del propio Olvideti.

title: Dinosaur Day
description: Pizza Steve's jealousy ruins Uncle Grandpa's Dinosaur Day celebration for Mr. Gus.

title: Superman Red vs Superman Blue
description: Luthor comes up with the means to separate each Justice Leaguer in two, one passive and good, the other aggressive and mean.

title: Make the Cut
description: Mega Man goes on a 24/7 heroing spree around the city, forcing Suna, Bert, Ashley, and Rush to deal with the problem at hand, Cut Man.

title: Two Lies, One Truth
description: As Lloyd unmasks Mystake for who she truly is, Emperor Garmadon embraces Harumi as his daughter of darkness. Meanwhile, Wu holds onto faith as he leads his friends into dangerous Oni territory in the hope of finding Firstbourne's nest

title: Showdown Part I
description: The Faction infiltrates Galvan in an attempt to destroy Azmuth.  (Introducing new Nemetrix aliens Omnivoracious & Vicetopus.)

title: Local Heroes/Pegatrix
description: Local Heroes: After the AO cause accidental destruction Dan's parents question whether the kids should be allowed to keep their Bakugan./Pegatrix: Lia disagrees with her new Bakugan Pegatrix on battle techniques but during a fierce fight Lia must rely on Pegatrix's battle savy.

title: Band of Outsiders
description: A gang of streetwise kids takes Baby Ice Bear under their wing.

title: Momsoon
description: Hedgehog gets a call during her radio show from someone who needs her help.

title: Hierro y piedra
description: Cole y Wu Joven intentan liberar a sus amigos, que han sido capturados por una tribu de Cazadores de Dragones. Mientras tanto en Ninjago, Lloyd se reúne con unos viejos amigos que quizás sean aliados valiosos contra el Emperador Garmadon.

title: Salvando a Faith
description: Lloyd y su equipo planean tomar el control del Oni Titan. Mientras tanto en el Primer Reino, los Ninja caen en las garras del Barón de Hierro y un viejo maestro regresa.

title: Mother of All Cards
description: Chef attempts to trick the kids into making his mother gifts after he forgets Mother's Day.

title: P.L.O.T. Device
description: When boredom levels in the castle hit dangerously high levels, Dr. Fox conveniently introduces her P.L.O.T. Device. When pressed, this device alters reality to make it more exciting. Richard warns that this might be dangerous, but no one listens. It's not long till he is proven correct and life in the castle becomes dangerously exciting.

title: Home on the Run/Top Slot
description: Home on the Run: We are introduced to Shun's mysterious backstory, his relationship with his industrialist father and desire for a closer knit family./Top Slot: Dan and Shun butt heads on how best to make the AO a real team amidst growing threats including the mysterious Shargo Ronin.

title: Ben Again
description: When Eon causes 11-year old Ben swap minds with teen Ben, it's up to Gwen, Rook, and Professor Paradox to set things straight.  (Featuring Eon and Professor Paradox.)

title: Green Destiny
description: The Ninja finally return home and unite to stop Emperor Garmadon, forcing Lloyd to make a decision that will forever change Ninjago.

title: Which Watch
description: After a battle with Kevin gets mysteriously cut short, Ben turns his attention to one upping Gwen at Space Camp. But, when his arch-nemesis, Kevin, returns with his sights strangely set on his cousin, our hero must uncover who is really behind it all, Charmcaster!

title: Roundabout Part 2
description: Forever Knight, with an over-clocked Time Machine in his grasp and a group of super- baddies by his side, is close to conquering all of history, but a certain hero with a team of 10 aliens on his side has other plans— foiling Forever Knight at every twist and turn in time!

title: Dream of Love
description: Tree Trunks is courted by an oinking suitor, but much to Jake's dismay, this interferes with her baking habits.

title: Bottle Catch
description: Apple and Onion's favorite game attracts some unexpected attention.

title: Keystone Motel
description: Steven, Greg and Garnet go on a road trip.

title: #Beeline
description: When she stumbles across a villainous plot to blow up a bridge, Bumblebee shies from the challenge of taking on the baddies and reaches out to her friends. But when the other heroes are all indisposed, it'll take every ounce of courage Bumblebee has to rise to the occasion … despite being the smallest of the bunch.

title: El camino dorado
description: El cuartel general de la resistencia es irrumpido y Lloyd lucha por no ser capturado. Mientras tanto, los Ninjas son capturados por Heavy-Metal, pero encuentran un aliado improbable.

title: Lessons for a Master
description: When Iron Baron forces Wu to retrieve the Dragon Armor, things don't go as planned. In Ninjago, Lloyd can only endure so much as he holds onto hope for the Ninjas' return.

title: Los Vegetales
description: Gumball y Darwin solo quieren holgazanear todo el día, pero terminan teniendo que salvar al resto de la familia.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Galactic Wonder
description: Wonder Woman has won student of the month at Super Hero High again!  As a special surprise Principal Waller has flown in Wonder Woman's mother, Queen Hippolyta, for a visit. Queen Hippolyta is not happy with what she finds and demands that Wonder Woman return to school at the island paradise of Themyscira. Hoping to take her mind off of her troubles with her mother Wonder Woman, Batgirl and Supergirl decide to investigate a strange electromagnetic anomaly. Their investigation leads them to the hideout of Lena Luthor where they discover a plot between her and Eclipso to transform the planet Earth into a new version of Gemworld!  The girls will have to split up to find the generators scattered around the planet and destroy them. They'll also have to overcome Lena's new breed of mood altering Kryptomites to save the day and convince Queen Hippolyta that Super Hero High is the best school for Wonder Woman!

title: A Star is Blossom
description: When Bubbles gets the lead in the school play, Blossom's jealousy consumes her.

title: Como construir un dragon
description: Mientras Lloyd y los rebeldes celebran su exitoso golpe contra el Emperador Garmadon, en el Reino de Oni y Dragón, los Ninjas se aventuran con un elaborado escape de las garras del Barón de Hierro y sus Cazadores de Dragones.

title: Store 23
description: While out looking for the elusive 23rd Mr. Smoothy's store with Blukic and Driba, Ben meets an alternate version of himself. (Guest-starring Aziz Ansari as Ben 23.)

title: Career Opportunities/Punch the Clock
description: Career Opportunities: After defeating Magnus the AO get an offer of employment from a surprising source Philomena Dusk!/Punch the Clock: During a commercial to celebrate their joining the AAAnimus team Dan and the AO rebel before they sellout.

title: T.G.I.S
description: The Secret Saturdays come to Bellwood to investigate a rash of chupacabra attacks.

title: Origin of Species
description: Origin of Species, Part 1: Dan meets his partner Bakugan Drago for the first time and we learn about the incident that happened on Earth twelve years ago./Origin of Species, Part 2: Dan and friends win the Bakugan Battle, firmly establishing the Awesome Ones as our heroes and Bakugan Brawlers.

title: Buggin' the Buggs
description: Team Tennyson travel to the Chrysalen Institute for some hot yoga and good vibes, only to find that the Bugg Brothers are on vacation, too, but are the sneaky insectoids really on holiday, or just cooking up yet another silly, yet high stakes scheme?

title: The Real Orangins!
description: Robin tries again to tell the real origin story of the Teen Titans.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Soother or Later
description: A terrified Duncan, who's afraid of lightning, learns it's even harder to break back into school than it was to break out when he finally escapes and finds himself in a dark alley with Izzy during a thunderstorm.

title: Blade of Grass
description: Finn and Jake decide it's time for Finn to get a new sword. Finn reluctantly buys a grass sword from a mysterious old man, but the sword turns out to be cursed! And unfortunately for our hero, all sales are final.

title: Sneeze Guard
description: Oscar and Hedgehog must work with the witches to cure Alice's camp-threatening illness.

title: The Parents
description: After accidentally bumping into each other in the grocery aisle, Nicole and her parents have it out. The Wattersons discover why Nicole and her parents haven't been on speaking terms for so long. The kids decide to bring about a reunion, in order to secure that backlog of birthday and holiday presents...

title: Belson's Sleepover
description: Belson invites Clarence and friends to a sleepover party, with a catch: whoever can survive the night's pranks and scares will win Belson's old Acedia game system!

title: Pachydermus Packard and the Camp of Fantasy
description: A doctor orders Mr. Pachydermus to have an adventure, so he attends the Warriors' super-annoying, "Fantasy Camp"!

title: Donut Factory Holiday
description: The guys have to return a VHS copy of their favorite terrible movie or else pay a huge late fee.

title: Falafel's Fun Day
description: When Falafel decides to pack up and leave the city, Apple and Onion have to convince him to stay or they'll have to leave too.

title: Dodge This
description: The park guys want to win a dodge ball tournament.

title: Chalmers Santiago
description: While Clarence spends a lazy Saturday playing 8-bit adventure game Dragon's Cusp, Mary asks him to return some mail to the guy across the street Chalmers Santiago, whom they've never seen. Clarence makes it his mission to befriend the mysterious neighbor, only to find out it's someone he knows quite well.

title: Snaketastrophy
description: The Serpentine attack on NINJAGO City is seen from an unexpected perspective - entirely in the style of a live newscast delivered by Gayle Gossip and her cameraman.

title: Know Your Fusion
description: Steven and the Gems delve deep into what makes a fusion so special.

title: Primogenita
description: El Emperador Garmadon ha tomado el control de Ciudad Ninjago donde Lloyd se retira hacia las sombras. Mientras tanto, los otros Ninjas y Wu Joven quedan varados en el Reino de Oni y Dragón y descubren que no están solos.

title: All Aboard the Space Train
description: In a strange turn of events, the JLA enlist the help of Space Cabbie and Jonah Hex to stop the hijacking of an intergalactic space train.

title: Hide and Secrets
description: Desperate for answers about Namagem, Mega Man decides to break into his father's lab, which leaves Suna exposed to the vengeful robot.

title: The Evolution of Craig
description: Craig rescues a tadpole and decides to raise him into a level 100 frog!

title: Radio Free NinjaGo
description: Lloyd must find his voice as he leads a small resistance to capture the airwaves in Ninjago City. Meanwhile in the First Realm, Iron Baron takes the Ninja on a dragon hunt.

title: Imaginary Fiend/Cootie Gras
description: Imaginary Fiend: The new boy in school has a special friend nobody else can see. When this imaginary friend begins destroying the class, the girls must imagine how to stop him./Cootie Gras: Mojo observes that everyone is staying away from little Harry Pitt because he has cooties. So Mojo concocts a plan to keep the girls away by using this cootie-covered boy as bait.

title: El Paseo en Autobus de Pancake
description: Manzana y Cebollín suben a un autobús que da un tour guiado como parte de su plan para recuperar el zapato de Manzana.

title: Panic in the Lighthouse
description: When Chaotique breaks into Dr. Light's lab, Mega Man must shut down his frenemy and the lab's defenses before either of them gets destroyed!

title: Midnight Madness
description: When the Rustbucket breaks down outside the largest mall in the U.S., it seems Ben and Gwen will have the time of their lives in the mall. That is until they run into an evil hypnotist entertaining the crowd, who puts Ben under hypnosis, causing him to sleepwalk at night and help him steal things. And when the hypnotist discovers certain aliens are now helping him, he exploits them for his grand plan of hypnotizing hundreds of people so they'll be under his demented control forever. Ben must figure out how to break the spell he's under and stop this evil plan.

title: #LaDulceJusticia - Segunda parte
description: Cuando seis chicas comunes y corrientes descubren que cada una tiene un poder extraordinario diferente, deciden unir fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis en la parte 2 del episodio estreno.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Mr. Moon/What's Wrong with Dan
description: Mr. Moon: Wynton finds a new Bakugan who proves difficult to control but things get more complicated when Col. Tripp seizes control of Trox./What's Wrong with Dan: With "Dan" behaving strangely toward the AO Lightning sniffs out the truth- an impostor!

title: Bao Bao's Revenge
description: When Mao Mao's old partner threatens the kingdom, his friends will need to learn about his past in order to protect the present.

title: Lying Around the House/Bubble Boy
description: Lying Around The House: The girls tell little white lies that turn into a big, bad problem./Bubble Boy: Realizing that the only way to beat the Rowdyruff Boys is to join them, Bubbles takes Boomer's place in this rough-and-tumble band of boys.

title: The Gauntlet Part 2
description: As Dr. Light and Suna turn the Robot Masters against each other, Mega Man defeats and unmasks his arch nemeses, Lord Obsidian, who turns out to be Sgt. Night in disguise, and finally learns the identity of Namagem, Mega Man's long lost twin brother!

title: Dos mentiras una verdad
description: Cuando Lloyd desenmascara y revela la identidad de Mystake, el Emperador Garmadon acepta a Harumi como su hija de la oscuridad. Mientras tanto, Wu se aferra a su fe al llevar a sus amigos hacia territorios Oni peligrosos esperando encontrar el nido de la Primogénita.

title: #SheMightBeGiant
description: Karen Beecher is always getting picked on at school, but when the local mall is attacked by a monstrous supervillain called Giganta, she discovers that tiny Bumblebee might be the only one small enough to save the day.

title: The Great Fossil Rush
description: JP finds a fossil in the Creek which quickly causes the landscape to change.

title: Iron & Stone
description: Cole and Young Wu attempt to free their friends, who have been taken captive by a tribe of Dragon Hunters. Meanwhile in Ninjago, Lloyd is reunited with some old friends who may prove valuable allies against Emperor Garmadon.

title: El Rival
description: Volvemos a la época en la que Anaís era una bebé recién nacida, y los celos de Gumball y Darwin desatan una guerra de bebés.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Bully for You/Trolling for Laughs
description: Bully for You: The AO must handle a neighborhood bully who is using his Bakugan to pick on the local kids./Trolling for Laughs: Wynton's constant practical jokes wear thin on his Bakugan Trox so the Bakugan decide to teach him a lesson.

title: Monster Weather
description: Max takes the kids to a drought stricken Chicago to see his favorite golden oldie band perform at a huge music festival. Once there, our heroes cross paths with a deranged weatherman.

title: Destino verde
description: Los Ninjas regresan por fin a casa y se unen para detener al Emperador Garmadon, obligando a Lloyd a tomar una decisión que cambiará por siempre a Ninjago.

title: Una Nueva Vida
description: Manzana y Cebollín abandonan sus hogares y se mudan a la ciudad, donde se conocen por primera vez.

title: Ancient History
description: While Aspheera pursues revenge on the "Treacherous Deceiver" who betrayed her, the ninja make a startling discovery.
